high_descs: Turn to the left and then to the right to find the coffee maker.
Pick up the fork from the counter.
Take the fork to the sink on the left.
Put the fork in the sink.
Find another fork in your hand.
Place the fork in the sink.
Walk to the coffee machine immediately to the left.
Pick up the fork on the counter top by the coffee machine.
Walk to the sink just to the left.
Put the fork in the sink basin.
Pick up the fork on the counter top to the left of the sink.
Put that fork into the sink basin too, to the left of the first fork.
anns.task_desc: Move two forks from the counter top to the sink.

high_descs: Go to the coffee machine to the left of the fridge,
Pick up the fork in front of the coffee machine.
Go to the sink to the left of the coffee machine.
Place the fork into the sink.
Pick up another fork from the drawer.
Place the fork into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place two forks into the sink.
